content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 850.10 - Dismissal of a matter

State Regulations

Civil matters.In addition to those circumstances set
forth in section
1250.10
(a) of
this Title, in the event that a petitioner fails to perfect an original special
proceeding within six months of the date of the service of the answer by
complying with the requirements of section
1250.13
(c)(2)
of
this Title, the matter shall be deemed dismissed without further
order. Notes
